data.value:
This is the Wasatch Front Consortium workshop scheduler. It is designed to create schedules for students and teachers in the participating schools of the Wasatch Front Consortium. You will need to have two Excel Files (.xlsx) for the workshop info and student requests.
It was created by Cody Henrichsen. To contact Cody please email him at cody.henrichsen@gmail.com
